  "texts": [
    "Owing to these advantages, NTMs have witnessed the exploration of numerous new methods and applications.",
    "Previously, Zhao et al (2021a) provided a review with a primary focus on the methods of NTMs.",
    "However, their review is beset by the following limitations: (i) Their method taxonomy is incomplete because they ignore several recently proposed NTM methods, such as NTMs with contrastive learning, cross-lingual NTMs, and dynamic NTMs.",
    "(ii) They omit the popular applications based on NTMs, developed for a wide range of downstream tasks.",
    "(iii) They lack in-depth discussions on the challenges inherent in NTMs."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Previously, Zhao et al (2021a) provided a review with a primary focus on the methods of NTMs."
  ]
}